review_text: The only thing I can say about this bank was that it is a very convenient bank if you are shopping in the area or visiting and you want to get some quick cash. They have a 24 hour ATM which is extremely convenient. There's also handicapped parking right in front of the bank as well as regular parking on the street for a limited time. I believe it said 15 minute parking so that you could use the bank. I love the decorations in the front and because it was Veterans Day the streets were decorated with lots of flags. So nice to see.
owner_reply: Thank you so much for leaving us a review! We are happy to hear about your positive experience with us, and we look forward to seeing you again!

review_text: Very helpful down to earth staff. The only downside to using Chelsea Groton Bank is that they are a smaller scale bank and only have locations available locally. Highly recommend regardless though
